OL,3,CAndy Burnham backs plans for tourist
OL,4,Ctax
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Mayor Andy Burnham
OL,7,Fis welcoming plans for a new tourist
OL,8,Ftax that would fund local projects.
OL,10,FUnder the proposals Mayors will be
OL,11,Fgiven the power to impose a "modest"
OL,12,Fcharge on visitors staying in hotels,
OL,13,Fbed and breakfasts, guest houses and
OL,14,Fholiday lets.
OL,16,FLocal Government Secretary Steve Reed
OL,17,Fsaid: "Tourists travel from near and
OL,18,Ffar to visit England's brilliant
OL,19,Fcities and regions.
OL,26,@sD@]OUsD@dO]yD@GOU
