OL,6,FThe money raised is intended to be
OL,7,Finvested in transport, infrastructure
OL,8,Fand the visitor economy to potentially
OL,9,Fattract more visitors.
OL,11,FMr Burnham said: "I'm proud that
OL,12,Fnearly two million people from all
OL,13,Fover the world choose to visit Greater
OL,14,FManchester every year. The money they
OL,15,Fspend contributes about #9 billion
OL,16,Fannually to our economy, supporting
OL,17,Fover 100,000 jobs.
