OL,6,F"The levy will allow us to invest in
OL,7,Fthe infrastructure these visitors
OL,8,Fneed, like keeping our streets clean
OL,9,Fand enhancing our public transport
OL,10,Fsystem through later running buses and
OL,11,Ftrams, making sure every experience is
OL,12,Fa positive and memorable one."
OL,14,FCurrently some businesses in
OL,15,FManchester can charge an extra #1 per
OL,16,Fnight. The Manchester Accommodation
OL,17,FBusiness Improvement District (ABID)
OL,18,Fsays the fee 'improves the visitor
OL,19,Fexperience' to the city centre and
OL,20,F'support the growth of the visitor
OL,21,Feconomy'.
