OL,6,FAt the moment 74 hotels and short-stay
OL,7,Fserviced apartments charge the fee.
OL,9,FIn Liverpool 83 hotels in the city are
OL,10,Fpart of a 'hotel levy' approved by the
OL,11,Fcity's Business Improvement District.
OL,13,FUnder the new plans it will be the
OL,14,FRegional Mayors who make the decisions
OL,15,Fabout what businesses are included in
OL,16,Fthe tourist tax and how the money is
OL,17,Fspent.
