OL,6,FKate Nicholls, chairwoman of industry
OL,7,Fbody UKHospitality, warned the
OL,8,F"damaging holiday tax" could cost the
OL,9,Fpublic up to #518 million, adding:
OL,10,F"Make no mistake ` this cost will be
OL,11,Fpassed directly on to consumers, drive
OL,12,Finflation and undermine the
OL,13,FGovernment's aim to reduce the cost of
OL,14,Fliving."
OL,16,FThe decision to give mayors the power
OL,17,Fcomes ahead of the budget.
